SafeWatch - Real-Time Safety App
(Flutter + Firebase)

SafeWatch is a real-time personal safety app built using Flutter and Firebase.
It includes authentication, live location tracking, SOS alerts, emergency contacts, and a modern glass-style UI.

This project was built from scratch as a full-stack capability showcase.

Features
Authentication System
Login, Register, Logout

Auto-login with Firebase Auth persistence

Role selection screen

AuthGate for protected routes

Production-ready routing flow

Navigation System
Centralised AppRouter

Clean, consistent route structure:
/auth, /login, /register, /role, /home, /map, /sos, /profile, /alerts

Home Dashboard (Glass UI)
Modern dashboard layout

Profile header

Quick actions

Safety status card

Recent alerts feed

Large SOS button

Map removed from home for cleaner UX

Real-Time Map System
Google Maps integration

Live user location

Ready for multi-user tracking

Routing connected

